==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inappropriate
<hw>In`ap*pro"pri*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
instrument (<xex>to</xex>); not appropriate; unbecoming; unsuitable; not
specially fitted; -- followed by <xex>to</xex> or <xex>for</xex>.</def>
-- <wordforms><wf>In`ap*pro"pri*ate*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>In`ap*pro"pri*ate*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inapt</ent>⟦br⟧
